title: create_sibling_gitlab() incompatible with present gitlab package version
body:

  Stored in directory: /home/mih/.cache/pip/wheels/aa/8f/5a/8bf3dfd89952ee0af40ace9421d68b4f03d949bac395b164ef
Successfully built gitlab

Successfully installed gitlab-1.0.2

% datalad create-sibling-gitlab --site inm7 --name jugit --project inm7/datasets/ukbiobank --publish-depends dataladstore-storage --access ssh
[ERROR  ] module 'gitlab' has no attribute 'config' [create_sibling_gitlab.py:__init__:521] (AttributeError)

The last working version is unknown.
